---
// imports
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

import IT from '../../img/icons/IT_B.png';
import GB from '../../img/icons/GB_B.png';

const {
  title = "My Astro Blog",
  description = "My musings about the Astro framework",
  image,
  frontmatter,
  robots,
} = Astro.props;
---

<Layout {title} {description} {image} {frontmatter} {robots}>
  <div class="container max-w-[1000px] mx-auto my-4 min-h-screen">
    <h1 class="title mt-16 mb-4 font-bold text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl">ABOUT US!</h1>
    <p class="georgia font-normal text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black my-8 first-letter:uppercase flex">
      <span class="font-bold font-condensed mr-2 mb-2 text-3xl md:text-4xl">
        <img src={IT} alt="Image" role="img" width="100" height="100">  
      </span> 
      Trstkills nasce come un gruppo di amici che condividono la stessa
      passione. trstkills Ã¨ un brand emergente che riguarda il mondo dello
      street art e della bmx, ci troviamo tutti i giorni preso lo skatepark di
      sangiacomo a trieste, al momento la bmx viene considerata poco, speriamo
      di poter organizzare qualche evento in futuro per far conoscere questo
      sport
    </p>
    <p class="georgia font-normal text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black my-8 first-letter:uppercase flex">
      <span class="font-bold font-condensed mr-2 mb-2 text-3xl md:text-4xl">
        <img src={GB} alt="Image" role="img" width="100" height="100">    
      </span> 
      Trstkills was born as a group of friends who share the same
      passion. trstkills is an emerging brand that concerns the world of street
      art and bmx, we meet every day at the sangiacomo skatepark in trieste, at
      the moment bmx is not considered much, we hope to be able to organize some
      event in the future to make this sport known
    </p>

    <div class="container mx-auto min-h-full">
      <div>
        <h1 class="georgia mt-16 text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl">Our crew on INSTA: check it out!</h1>
        <a href="" target="_blank" role="link">
          <!-- <img src={insta} width="250" height="250" alt="Instagram" role="img"> -->
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
